```
Q1: user_id in labels = cardinality bomb = OOM crash loop
    Fix: metric_relabel_configs to drop, sample_limit as safety net
    Monitor: prometheus_tsdb_head_series

Q2: histogram_quantile ALWAYS needs rate() + sum by (le)
